Distribution: Currently known from the type locality “Pangnamdim, Dadung” [Nam Tamai Valley (
27 ° 42 'N
,
97 ° 54 'E
), The Triangle, Upper Burma ] (
Smith, 1940
). Pangnamdim is located in Kachin State, northern Myanmar at ca. 1,166 m asl. Dadung could not be located on gazetteers but may refer to Dazung Dam (ca. 1,230 m asl) nearby Pangnamdim. A population of this species has recently been found in eastern Arunachal Pradesh, northeast India (
Kunte and Manthey, 2009
).
